title: Sidewall, 1920–40
creditline: Gift of Mark Bitter, Robert Bitter, Ward Bitter, and Tami Bitter Cook
description: Sanitary paper. Very classically styled architectural border. Quatrefoil on a boss, centered between two fluted bosses. A band of floral motifs along either edge. Printed in tans and green on off-white ground. Printed three across. Varnished.

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall, 1920–40.
1920–40. Machine-printed. Gift of Mark Bitter, Robert Bitter, Ward Bitter, and Tami Bitter Cook. 1992-139-88.
